      "description": "Output buffer for the meaning of the communication error."
    },
    {
      "name": "bufferLen",
      "type": "",
      "description": "Capacity of the output buffer."
    }
  ],
  "return": "Number of characters written to the buffer.",
  "example": {
    "description": [],
    "code": "...\nif (0 == TestWaitForDiagResponse( req, 2000))\n{\n  char errStr[100];\n  err = DiagGetLastCommunicationError();\n  DiagGetCommunicationErrorString( err, errStr, elcount(errStr));\n  write(\"LastCommunicationError=%d - %s\", err, errStr);\n}"
  },
